    <p>
        <button type="button" onclick="location.href='/book/write'">등록</button>
        <button type="button" onclick="location.href='/book/list'">리스트</button>
        &nbsp&nbsp 조회수 : ${book.book_count} &nbsp&nbsp
        평점 : ${score}
